Attribution / 歸屬聲明
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

This translation patch is a derivative work. Upstream sources:

1. LimbusTraditionalMandarin/storyline (storyline branch)
   https://github.com/LimbusTraditionalMandarin/storyline
   License: CC BY-NC-SA 4.0
   Used as: base Traditional Chinese translation for Canto 1–9 and existing
   Intervallo content.

2. louzhee/LocalizeLimbusIT (Italian Espresso Office, Release v.1.0.2)
   https://github.com/louzhee/LocalizeLimbusIT
   Used as: English source text for Canto 9.5.1 "Fili Intrecciati" content
   not yet translated by LTM.

3. Claude Code subagents (Anthropic)
   Automated translation of gaps from English/Korean → Traditional Chinese
   (Taiwan), with glossary consistency enforcement against LTM conventions.

